title: Ep 64: Transition
description: "People changes" to quote Steve the great Philosopher. What to do when you're going thru a major life change? Panic? Yes. Have anxiety? Yes. Drink wine? YES. All of the above. Peep this episode as I talk about what to do about the necessity of transitions.
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
